security.current-risks:
localStorage tokens in both frontends;
deployment scripts with weak defaults and sshpass;
remote credentials may be materialized during install/deploy;
git remote token leak existed in local clone during analysis.

quality-reality.implemented-tooling:
pytest config in backend pyproject;
ruff and mypy configured in backend;
frontend build scripts present;
backend tests exist for vpn, migrations, telegram auth, billing security.

quality-reality.missing-or-incomplete:
CI pipeline in repository;
repeatable full-stack local verification;
frontend unit/e2e tests in repo;
disciplined Alembic migration workflow.
